                            <comment id="14066939" author="lefty@hortonworks.com" created="Fri, 18 Jul 2014 21:52:16 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;... metadata for the connection is registered in beeline. User may close it or try reconnect it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should this be documented in the wiki?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14068119" author="navis" created="Mon, 21 Jul 2014 02:33:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=leftylev&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;leftylev&quot;&gt;leftylev&lt;/a&gt; Seemed not. User can decide action by just seeing the current state in prompt.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
